entry.name: target_records & target date
entry.sql: update log.staging_log set target_records = (select count(1) from staging.${table_name}), target_date = now() where table_name = '${table_name}'

entry.name: logical
entry.sql: update log.staging_log set logical = case when source_records = target_records then 'success' else 'To Be Evaluated' end where table_name = '${table_name}'
